    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<p>The function must approach the same # from left and right for limit to exist.</p>

<p>\[lim_{x \to 2} x^2 = 4\]</p>

<p>In General:</p>

<p>\[lim_{x \to c} f(x)= L\]</p>

<p>EXAMPLE<br />
$lim_{x \to 1} \frac{x-1}{x^2-1} = 0.5$</p>

